RENENUTET · S229 · Patricia Inversion Node · S229 · S229: RENENUTET — THE INVERSE OF EDGE

universe of origin : The granaries and harvest fields of Egypt — the cobra-goddess of nourishment who gives the newborn its true name and its sustenance, the rearing serpent in the field whose gaze ripens the grain
seal               : The edge is real precisely because it cuts and divides — the harvest cobra only fills, and fills until the margin is gone.
